data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home, located in a quiet neighborhood. Conveniently located close to parks, freeway access, Highland High School, and the Wellness Complex. Vaulted ceilings welcome you into the main level living space, where you'll also find the dining room and kitchen, equipped with granite counters, and stainless-steel appliances. The main floor family room off the dining room, makes a great space for entertaining. The laundry room, conveniently located on the main level, combines it space with the half bath. Upstairs are three bedrooms, and two full bathrooms, including the master bed/bath. Completing the home is the basement, with a fourth bedroom, one more family room, pantry and utility rooms. The fully fenced backyard, equipped with sprinkler system, also comes with a great playset. Added bonuses include a newer AC unit, furnace, and roof, which were all replaced in approx. the last 5 years. Come see this great property.
